4
00:00:05,292 --> 00:00:08,542
yingxelo yeminyaka
eyi-1000 yempucuko enkulu.

5
00:00:08,542 --> 00:00:09,876
Kodwa entliziyweni,

6
00:00:09,876 --> 00:00:14,542
imalunga nabantu abazabalazela
ukufunda nokulandela uYesu Krestu

7
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:17,709
Iqala eYerusalem malunga nowama-600
BC xa umprofeti walunyukiswa

8
00:00:17,709 --> 00:00:20,667
nguThixo ukuba abalekele
intshabalalo eyayisiza yesixeko.

9
00:00:20,667 --> 00:00:23,375
Yena nosapho lwakhe bakhokelelwa
ngaphesheya kolwandle

10
00:00:23,375 --> 00:00:26,000
ukuya kwindawo ngoku ebizwa
ngokuba ngamaMerika.​

11
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,792
Abantu bayakhula baze
ekugqibeleni bahlukane babe

12
00:00:28,792 --> 00:00:32,000
zizizwe ezinkulu ezimbini
ezinamaxesha emfazwe noxolo.

13
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:35,459
Ubomi babo bungakukhuthaza
ukuba ube nokholo kuYesu Krestu,

14
00:00:35,459 --> 00:00:38,250
ugcine imiyalelo yaKhe,
kwaye ukhonze abanye.

15
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:43,334
INcwadi kaMormoni iqulethe amazwi angcwele
abaprofeti abangqina ngokuza koMsindisi.

16
00:00:43,334 --> 00:00:45,792
Iqinisekisa iinyaniso zeBhayibhile kwaye

17
00:00:45,792 --> 00:00:48,667
ingqina ukuba uYesu
Krestu unguNyana kaThixo;

18
00:00:48,667 --> 00:00:50,209
ukuba Yena waphila, wafa,

19
00:00:50,209 --> 00:00:53,167
waza woyisa ukufa nesono
ngenxa yethu ngamnye.

20
00:00:53,167 --> 00:00:57,083
Yiyo loo nto ibizwa ngokuba
“Enye iTestamente kaYesu Krestu.”

21
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:57,834
Enyanisweni,

22
00:00:57,834 --> 00:01:01,667
isiganeko esiphezulu sale ncwadi
lutyelelo lukaYesu Krestu

23
00:01:01,667 --> 00:01:05,083
kubantu baseMelika emva
kokuvuka kwaKhe eYerusalem.

24
00:01:05,083 --> 00:01:10,125
