kwaye usikelela abantwana babo.

25
00:01:10,125 --> 00:01:12,042
Kodwa eso sisiqalo nje sebali.

26
00:01:12,042 --> 00:01:15,292
Elona futhe lokwenyani
leNcwadi kaMormoni yindlela

27
00:01:15,292 --> 00:01:18,792
enokukunceda ngayo neengxaki
ojongene nazo namhlanje.

28
00:01:18,792 --> 00:01:21,125
Unokufumana intuthuzelo, ulwalathiso,

29
00:01:21,125 --> 00:01:24,751
nokufunda indlela yokuba
ngumntu ongcono nowonwabileyo.

30
00:01:24,751 --> 00:01:26,125
Ngaphezu kwako konke,

31
00:01:26,125 --> 00:01:30,083
ungasondela kufuphi ngakumbi
kuMsindisi wakho uYesu Krestu.

